HEADWORD: Incalculable
<hw>In*cal"cu*la*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>in-</ets> not + <ets>calculable</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>incalculable</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not capable of being calculated;
beyond calculation; very great; <as>as, his action did
<ex>incalculable</ex> harm</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>In*cal"cu*la*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
<wf>In*cal"cu*la*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
